# How will I learn about scheduled online classes?

Information regarding the scheduled online classes will be provided to you in
the form of:

  1. Messages sent to your student email address through the Virtual University system;
  2. Announcements published in the Virtual University system;
  3. Direct email messages sent by course instructors;
  4. Directly through the Microsoft Teams platform – in the case of groups who have already participated in classes using this platform.
  5. Our postgraduate course participants will also receive information published also on Podio.

